FBIS3-19967 "drweu058__a94013" FBIS-WEU-94-058-A Document Type:Daily Report 25 March 1994 ANNEX Germany Yeltsin To Attend Farewell Ceremony for Russians AU2503103694 Hamburg DPA in German 0921 GMT 25 Mar 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU2503103694 Hamburg DPA Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Erfurt (DPA) -- On 31 August, Russian President Boris Yeltsin will come to Weimar to attend the farewell ceremony for the last Russian soldier. FRG Chancellor Helmut Kohl (Christian Democratic Union) is also expected to participate in the festive act in the national theater of the city, the state chancellery reported in Erfurt on Friday [25 March]. The German-Russian friendship of the last century is to be recalled and continued in the city of classical writers with this commemoration ceremony, which is accompanied by a cultural program. Kohl provided the initiative for the farewell ceremony in Weimar, it was stated.
